response.original_title: All Dolled Up: Love Dolls and Those Who Love Them
response.overview: All Dolled Up is a documentary about high end love dolls, and the men and women who own them. Light-hearted but serious, this documentary is the first to dive deeply into this unique culture. You'll be surprised with how well these dolls are taken care of...
response.title: All Dolled Up: Love Dolls and Those Who Love Them
